learning_outcomes.en:
On completion of the course the student:
knows essential vocabulary in the field of primary school and basic school education and comprehends speciality-related texts (B1language level);
can discuss about educational issues within the range of the vocabulary acquired;
is able to paraphrase and refer to the educational texts;
is able to compile written and oral presentations on the basis of literature in the field of primary school and basic school education.

learning_outcomes.et:
Üliõpilane tunneb alg- ja põhihariduse pedagoogika alast sõnavara ja suudab tekste mõista (B1 keeletase);
üliõpilane suudab arutleda haridusalastel teemadel omandatud sõnavara ulatuses;
üliõpilane suudab parafraseerida ja refereerida haridusalaseid tekste;
üliõpilane oskab koostada suulise ettekande alg- ja põhihariduse erialakirjanduse põhjal.
